				<div class="featured-image">
			<a href="http://www.ssarl.org/being-a-grandpa-is-great/" title="Being a grandpa is great">
				<img width="280" height="210" src="http://www.ssarl.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Being-a-grandpa-is-great-280x210.jpg" class="attachment-half-width size-half-width wp-post-image" alt="Being a grandpa is great" srcset="http://www.ssarl.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Being-a-grandpa-is-great-280x210.jpg 280w, http://www.ssarl.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Being-a-grandpa-is-great-300x225.jpg 300w, http://www.ssarl.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Being-a-grandpa-is-great-768x576.jpg 768w, http://www.ssarl.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Being-a-grandpa-is-great-660x495.jpg 660w, http://www.ssarl.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Being-a-grandpa-is-great.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 280px) 100vw, 280px" />			</a>
		</div>
		
		<p>Now I know that people sway you shouldn’t wish your life away but in my humble opinion there are points in life which are simply better and we are therefore much more likely to look forward to than others. Going right back to the earliest of starts, when you were a kid things were great. &#8230;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.ssarl.org/being-a-grandpa-is-great/" class="more-link">More <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
